emucap-live.lua is a Lua script loaded at runtime by Mesen2 (via a command-line
argument); it is not compiled or linked into the Mesen2 binary, so under the
interpreter rule it is not a derivative of Mesen2 (GPL-3.0). It is licensed as the
project default, GPL-2.0-or-later. If a "bindings"-based derivative reading were
adopted, this single adapter would instead be GPL-3.0. See ../../NOTICE.

